{
  "text": "In the S-HD subgroup treated with the vitamin E-modified filter, vitamin E and lipid composition in terms of the essential free fatty acids (arachidonic, linoleic, and linolenic acid), were measured in plasma and RBC lipid extracts, as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
